=== 遠古時代 ===
[[File:PEbers_c41-bc.jpg|thumb]]的[[Ebers_Papyrus|Ebers Papyrus]] (''c.'' 1550 BC) 描述了數百種植物藥物的使用。<ref name="Sumner-2000-p17"/>]]

在古代的蘇美爾地區，數百種藥用植物，包括[[沒藥|沒藥]]和[[鴉片|鴉片]]被列在粘土片上。

古埃及紙莎草紙列出了[[蘆薈|蘆薈]]、[[大麻|大麻]]、[[蓖麻|蓖麻]]、[[大蒜|大蒜]]、[[杜松|杜松]]、[[風茄|風茄]]等800多種植物藥物。<ref name="Sumner-2000-p17">{{cite book |author=Sumner, Judith |title=The Natural History of Medicinal Plants |url=https://archive.org/details/naturalhistoryof0000sumn |publisher=Timber Press|year=2000 |isbn=0-88192-483-0|page=[https://archive.org/details/naturalhistoryof0000sumn/page/17 17]}}</ref>從古代到現在，阿闥婆吠陀，里瓦吠陀和埃伯斯紙草文稿中記載的[[阿育吠陀|阿育吠陀]]已經使用了數百種具有藥理活性的藥草和香料，如[[薑黃|薑黃]]，其中含有[[薑黃素|薑黃素]]。<ref name=Aggarwal2007>{{cite journal |authors=Aggarwal, B. B.; Sundaram, C.; Malani, N.; Ichikawa, H. |title=Curcumin: the Indian solid gold |journal=Adv. Exp. Med. Biol. |volume=595 |issue=|pages=1–75 |year=2007 |pmid=17569205 |doi=10.1007/978-0-387-46401-5_1 |series=Advances in Experimental Medicine and Biology |isbn=978-0-387-46400-8}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Girish Dwivedi |first=Shridhar Dwivedi |year=2007 |title=History of Medicine: Sushruta – the Clinician – Teacher par Excellence |publisher=[[National_Informatics_Centre|National Informatics Centre]] |url=http://medind.nic.in/iae/t07/i4/iaet07i4p243.pdf |accessdate=8 October 2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010045900/http://medind.nic.in/iae/t07/i4/iaet07i4p243.pdf |archivedate=10 October 2008 |df= }}</ref>[[中國藥典|中國藥典]]、[[神農本草經|神農本草經]]記錄了[[麻風|麻風]]、[麻黃]和[[麻|麻]]等[[chaulmoogra|chaulmoogra]]植物藥。<ref name="Sumner-2000-p18">{{cite book |author=Sumner, Judith |title=The Natural History of Medicinal Plants |url=https://archive.org/details/naturalhistoryof0000sumn |publisher=Timber Press |year=2000 |isbn=0-88192-483-0 |page=[https://archive.org/details/naturalhistoryof0000sumn/page/18 18]}}</ref> This was expanded in the [[Tang_Dynasty|Tang Dynasty]] ''[[Yaoxing_Lun|Yaoxing Lun]]''.<ref>{{cite book |author=Wu, Jing-Nuan |title=An Illustrated Chinese Materia Medica |publisher=Oxford University Press |year=2005 |isbn=978-0-19-514017-0 |page=6 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=H9Q8agQrJR0C&pg=PA6 |access-date=2018-03-08 |archive-date=2018-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713104308/https://books.google.com/books?id=H9Q8agQrJR0C&pg=PA6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在公元前四世紀，[亞里士多德]的學生[[Theophrastus|Theophrastus]]寫了第一本有系統的植物學文本，'''Historia Plantarum (Theophrastus)'''。<ref name="philobio11">{{cite book|last=Grene |first=Marjorie |title=The philosophy of biology: an episodic history |year=2004 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |isbn=978-0-521-64380-1 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TJSGJjh8Jo8C&pg=PA11 |page=11}}</ref>在公元一世紀，希臘醫生[[迪奧科里斯|迪奧科里斯]]記錄了1000多種藥物配方，使用了'''De materia medica'''中的600多種藥用植物。 它仍然是關於草藥學的權威性參考，已超過1500年，進入17世紀。<ref name=Collins2000>{{cite book |author=Collins, Minta |title=Medieval Herbals: The Illustrative Traditions |publisher=University of Toronto Press |year=2000 |isbn=978-0-8020-8313-5 |page=32 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=s7c2EaxDYjUC&pg=PA32 |access-date=2018-03-08 |archive-date=2017-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215084545/https://books.google.com/books?id=s7c2EaxDYjUC&pg=PA32 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
