== 植物化學基礎 ==
{{further|植物化學}}
所有植物都產生化學化合物，這些化合物具有進化優勢，例如防禦食草動物，或者在[[水楊酸|水楊酸]]的例子中，作為植物防禦中的[[激素|激素]]。<ref name=USDAingredients/><ref>{{cite book | title = Salicylic Acid – A Plant Hormone |author1=Hayat, S. |author2=Ahmad, A.  |lastauthoramp=yes | isbn = 1-4020-5183-2| year = 2007 | publisher = Springer Science and Business Media}}</ref>這些植物化學物質具有作為藥物的潛力，如果科學證實，這些物質在藥用植物中的含量和已知的藥理活性是它們在現代醫學中使用的科學依據。<ref name=ahn/>例如，[[水仙|水仙]]（Narcissus）含有九組生物鹼，包括[[加蘭他敏|加蘭他敏]]，許可用於治療[[阿爾茨海默症|阿爾茨海默症]]。生物鹼是苦味和有毒的，並且濃縮在植物的部分，例如最容易被食草動物吃掉的莖; 他們也可以防止[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bastida |first1=Jaume |last2=Lavilla |first2=Rodolfo |last3=Viladomat |first3=Francesc Viladomat |editor1-last=Cordell |editor1-first=G. A. |title=Chemical and biological aspects of "Narcissus" alkaloids |journal=The Alkaloids: Chemistry and Biology |date=2006 |volume=63 |pages=87–179 |doi=10.1016/S1099-4831(06)63003-4 |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/6664419_Chemical_and_biological_aspects_of_Narcissus_alkaloids/file/79e415020c218c82b0.pdf |accessdate=17 March 2018 |series=The Alkaloids: Chemistry and Biology |isbn=9780124695634}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Galantamine |url=https://www.drugs.com/mtm/galantamine.html |publisher=Drugs.com |date=2017 |accessdate=17 March 2018 |archive-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014091614/https://www.drugs.com/mtm/galantamine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pmid=16437532 |year=2006 |author1=Birks |first1=J. |title=Cholinesterase inhibitors for Alzheimer's disease |journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews |issue=1 |pages=CD005593 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005593}}</ref>

藥用植物轉錄組學數據庫正在系統化藥用植物的現代知識，該數據庫於2011年為約30種物種的轉錄組提供了序列參考。<ref name='DK_herb'/>，藥理學活性的主要種類的植物化學物質如下所述，與包含它們的藥用植物的實例。<ref name="Angio" /><ref name=Cravotto/><ref name="meskin-2002-p123">{{cite book |author=Meskin, Mark S. |title=Phytochemicals in Nutrition and Health |publisher=CRC Press |year=2002 |isbn=978-1-58716-083-7 |page=123 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cJHsMALUDj0C&pg=PA123 |access-date=2018-10-14 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519093123/https://books.google.com/books?id=cJHsMALUDj0C&pg=PA123 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |authors=Springbob, Karen & Kutchan, Toni M. |chapter=Introduction to the different classes of natural products |editor=Lanzotti, Virginia |title=Plant-Derived Natural Products: Synthesis, Function, and Application |publisher=Springer |year=2009 |isbn=978-0-387-85497-7 |page=3 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Y8SpVXEng4QC&pg=PA3 |access-date=2018-10-14 |archive-date=2019-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520115940/https://books.google.com/books?id=Y8SpVXEng4QC&pg=PA3 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Elumalai">{{cite journal |last1=Elumalai |first1=A. |last2=Eswariah |first2=M. Chinna |title=Herbalism - A Review |journal=International Journal of Phytotherapy |date=2012 |volume=2 |issue=2 |pages=96–105 |url=http://www.phytotherapyjournal.com/File_Folder/96-105.pdf |author= |access-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217232814/http://www.phytotherapyjournal.com/File_Folder/96-105.pdf |archive-date=2017-02-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 生物碱 ===
{{further|生物鹼}}

具有生物活性成分的含氮[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]。一般具有强烈的效果，许多具有[[毒性|毒性]]（如麻黄碱等）。许多重要的药物皆是生物碱制品（如[[茶碱|茶碱]]），是现代[[制药|制药]]研究的重点。

生物鹼是一種苦味化學物質，在自然界中非常普遍，並且在許多藥用植物中常常有毒。<ref name=Aniszewski2007>{{cite book |author=Aniszewski, Tadeusz |title=Alkaloids – secrets of life|url=https://archive.org/details/alkaloidssecrets00anis_819 |location=Amsterdam |publisher=[[Elsevier|Elsevier]] |year=2007|isbn=978-0-444-52736-3 |page=[https://archive.org/details/alkaloidssecrets00anis_819/page/n200 182]}}</ref>有幾類具有不同作用方式的藥物，包括娛樂和藥物。不同類別的藥物包括阿托品，[[東莨菪鹼|東莨菪鹼]]和[[莨菪鹼|莨菪鹼]]（均來自茄科），<ref name="EMEA">{{cite web |title=Atropa Belladonna |url=http://www.ema.europa.eu/docs/en_GB/document_library/Maximum_Residue_Limits_-_Report/2009/11/WC500010731.pdf |publisher=The European Agency for the Evaluation of Medicinal Products |accessdate=26 February 2017 |date=1998 |archive-date=2018-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417200131/http://www.ema.europa.eu/docs/en_GB/document_library/Maximum_Residue_Limits_-_Report/2009/11/WC500010731.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>傳統醫學小蘗鹼（來自植物如[[小檗屬|小蘗]]和[[十大功勞|十大功勞]]）、[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]（[[咖啡屬|咖啡]]）、[[可卡因|可卡因]]（可口可樂）、[[麻黃鹼|麻黃鹼]]（麻黃）、嗎啡（鴉片罌粟）、尼古丁（煙草）、利血平（ Rauwolfia serpentina）、[[奎尼丁|奎尼丁]]和[[奎寧|奎寧]]（[[金雞納樹|金雞納樹]]）、[[長春胺|長春胺]]（[[小蔓長春花|小蔓長春花]]）和[[長春新鹼|長春新鹼]]（長春花）。<ref name="Elumalai"/><ref name="Gremigni">{{cite journal | last1 =Gremigni, etal.| first1=P.| year=2003| title =The interaction of phosphorus and potassium with seed alkaloid concentrations, yield and mineral content in narrow-leafed lupin (Lupinus angustifolius L.) | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-and-soil_2003-06_253_2/page/413| journal=[[Plant_and_Soil|Plant and Soil]] | volume=253| issue=2 | pages =413–427 | publisher=Springer | location=Heidelberg | jstor=24121197}}</ref>

